    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "A New Species Of Rhagoletis (Diptera, Tephritidae) From Switzerland, With Discussion Of Its Relationships Within The Genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6456142>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6456146> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6456142>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Palearctic species of Rhagoletis species similar to R. merzi, wings: a — R. zernyi; b — R. flavigenualis; c — R. merzi, sp. n.; d — R. bagheera; e — R. batava. Bands are marked as follows: A — apical, D — discal, SA — subapical, SB — subbasal. Red arrow shows connection of D and SA; cyan arrow shows cr — crescentic hyaline area. Scale: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6456142/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6456146>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Palearctic species of Rhagoletis species similar to R. merzi, epandrium and surstyli, posterior view (a–c) and spermatheca (d–f): a, d — R. batava; b, e — R. flavigenualis; c, f — R. merzi sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6456146/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

